                                            N√£o
                                        </label>
                                    </div>
                                    <textarea id="medicationDetails" placeholder="Se sim, quais medicamentos..." rows="2" class="form-input w-full rounded-lg px-4 py-3 focus:outline-none">${client.anamnesis?.medicationDetails || ''}</textarea>
                                </div>

                                <div>
                                    <label class="block text-white font-semibold mb-2">Possui alguma doen√ßa ou condi√ß√£o m√©dica?</label>
                                    <textarea id="medicalConditions" placeholder="Descreva condi√ß√µes m√©dicas relevantes..." rows="2" class="form-input w-full rounded-lg px-4 py-3 focus:outline-none">${client.anamnesis?.medicalConditions || ''}</textarea>
